      "content": "That's exactly the vibe I'm looking for. To really drive home the \"necessity\" of the mission for the audience, could you add a section where he compares their physical or mental temperament to something more \"orderly\"? Like, why their specific nature makes them naturally suited for labor or following strong leadership rather than making their own decisions? I want to emphasize that sense of natural hierarchy that was so common in those journals.",
